name: caduceo
text: I often wonder how to rate things. Onstad produces the highest volume of clever of any source I know on the internet. Therefore, it seems anything, no matter how paltry, should be voted a 5. Then I wonder, whats the point of the voting system? So, it leaves me confused.

name: evolume
text:
my rating system:

1 = i get mad and turn off the internets.
2 = i do not even grin slightly and maybe am a little annoyed or offended.
3 = i smile and perhaps add laughter to my internal dialog.
4 = i laugh out loud. a genuine LOL but not an ROFL.
5 = i can't stop laughing. i think of this strip days later and laugh while riding the bus such that people are giving me concerned looks. i buy the t-shirt and quote the strip at social gatherings such that people are giving me concerned looks.
